headline: ICE Launches Long European Union Bond Index Futures
summary: LONDON, December 10, 2024--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data today announced the launch of Long European Union (EU) Bond Index futures along with the first trades in the contract.
